dataset_id: MISR L1B3 Radiometric Camera-by-camera Cloud Mask Product subset for the RICO region V004
title: MISR L1B3 Radiometric Camera-by-camera Cloud Mask Product subset for the RICO region V004
summary: This file contains the Radiometric camera-by-camera Cloud Mask dataset over the RICO region. It is used to determine whether a scene is classified as clear or cloudy. A new parameter has been added to indicate dust over ocean. This version of the ESDT is used by MISR PGE 13.
